- In this task, we created a robot control panel on a web page utilizing HTML and PHP languages and XAMPP software. 
- A database was created on XAMPP software. 
- By the use of index.html file, the control panel page was formatted with four directional buttons, and an extra stop button was addtionally included. 
- connect.php and view.php files were used to make a connection between the control panel web page and the database to insert and retrieve data to and from the database. 
